Your code is currently asking whether a `JProperty` is a `JArray`.  The answer to that is always no.  `JProperty` does not derive from `JArray`.  (Both derive from `JToken`.) 

What you really want to be asking is whether the *value* of the `JProperty` is a `JArray`.

